### Variables — set @token after login
@host = https://localhost:7125
@token = paste_jwt_here

### Login (public) — default seed admin: admin / Admin@123 (see appsettings SeedAdmin)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Admin — create user (requires Admin JWT)
POST {{host}}/api/admin/create-user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jdoe",
  "password": "User@123",
  "role": "User"
}

### Admin — list users
GET {{host}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Attendance — check-in (office: 11.5564, 104.9282 — within 100m)
POST {{host}}/api/attendance/check-in
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 11.5564,
  "longitude": 104.9282
}

### Attendance — check-out (same; allowed only after 17:00 server local time per stored procedure)
POST {{host}}/api/attendance/check-out
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 11.5564,
  "longitude": 104.9282
}

### Attendance — my records
GET {{host}}/api/attendance/my-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
